<name>BRAKE BOOSTER</name>
<para id="RM000000SRO005X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="BR02N-06" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000000SRO005X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000000SRO005X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00003C900000">
<ptxt>INSPECT VACUUM CHECK VALVE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Inspect the vacuum check valve.</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>Slide the clip and disconnect the vacuum hose.</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>Remove the vacuum check valve.</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>Check that there is ventilation from the booster to the engine, and no ventilation from the engine to the booster. If the results are not as specified, replace the brake booster assembly.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C133436E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s3>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
